\v 4 Their descendantsÂŠ333978 \add âare very stubbornÂŠ333981 and hardheaded\add*. I'm sendingÂŠ333985 you to them, and you'll tell them that this is what the masterÂŠ333992 YahwehÂŠ333992 is saying to them.
