\v 1 ButÂŠ334625 you, humanity'sÂŠ334628 child, get yourselfÂŠ334631 a brickÂŠ334632 and place it \add âin frontÂŠ334635 of\add* you and carve YerushalemÂŠ334641 CityÂŠ334626 on it.
\v 2 ThenÂŠ334643 lay siegeÂŠ334645 against it, and buildÂŠ334646 forts against it. \add âBuild\add* an assault ramp up against it and make camps around it. Place batteringÂŠ334658 rams all around it.
