\p
\v 4 Then lie on your left sideÂŠ334693 and put the sin of the \add âIsraeliÂŠ334701 people\add* on it. You'll carry theirÂŠ334711 sin for the numberÂŠ334703 of daysÂŠ334704 you lie down \add as a sign\add* against them.
\v 5 I myself am assigningÂŠ334714 to you one day to represent each year of theirÂŠ334719 punishment: 390 daysÂŠ334721 \add lying on your left side\add*. In that way, you'll carry the \add âIsraeliÂŠ334729 people's\add* sin.
