\v 7 \add âKeep looking\add* towards YerushalemÂŠ334764, which is under siegeÂŠ334763, andÂŠ334761 with your arm baredÂŠ334768 \add like a warrior\add*, prophesyÂŠ334769 againstÂŠ334770 itÂŠ334770.
