\v 9 Take wheatÂŠ334793, barleyÂŠ334794, beansÂŠ334795, lentilsÂŠ334796, milletÂŠ334797, and speltÂŠ334798 for yourself, \add and\add* put them into a single container, and make breadÂŠ334806 for yourself according to the numberÂŠ334807 of days you'll lie onÂŠ334801 your sideâ\add yes,\add* you'll eat it for 390 days.
