\v 11 ThenÂŠ334837 you'll measureÂŠ334838 out half a litre of waterÂŠ334837 to drink each day, andÂŠ334837 you'll drink it atÂŠ334838 set times.
\v 12 You'll \add cook andÂŠ334851\add* eatÂŠ334850 \add @that breadÂŠ334848\add* as barleyÂŠ334849 cakes, butÂŠ334848 \add burn sun-dried\add* humanÂŠ334854 excrementÂŠ334853 to bake itÂŠ334855 over \add âwhile they're watching\add*.
