\v 12 ThenÂŠ336199 he \add âasked\add* me, âHumanity's child, do you see what the \add âIsraeliÂŠ336207\add* eldersÂŠ336206 are doingÂŠ336210 in the dark? Each one does this in his idol'sÂŠ336214 hidden roomÂŠ336213, becauseÂŠ336215 they say, âYahweh doesn't \add even\add* \add ânotice\add* us. Yahweh'sÂŠ336218 \add âabandonedÂŠ336221 this country\add*.â â
