\p
\v 1 \add âNow sing a mournful song for Yisrael's leaders,\add*
\v 2 saying:
\q1 âWho was your motherÂŠ341009? A lionessÂŠ341010âshe lived with a lion's son.
\q1 There among the youngÂŠ341015 lions, she rearedÂŠ341016 herÂŠ341017 cubs.
\q1
\v 3 She's the one who raised one of herÂŠ341021 cubs to become a youngÂŠ341022 lionâ
\q1 a lion who learnedÂŠ341024 to tear apart his victims,
\q1 andÂŠ341019 thenÂŠ341019 he devouredÂŠ341029 people.
\q1
