\p
\v 1 Then YahwehÂŠ343991 \add âgave\add* me \add another\add* messageÂŠ343989 onÂŠ343993 the 15th of January of the ninthÂŠ343994 yearÂŠ343993 \add since King Yoyakin (Jehoiachin) had been taken captive\add*.
\v 2 âHumanity's child, writeÂŠ344004 down \add âthe day and month\add* for yourselfÂŠ344007, because onÂŠ344024 this exact day, the Babylonian king \add âstarted his siege of\add* YerushalemÂŠ344023.\x + \xo 24:2: \xt 2Ki 25:1.\x*
\v 3 \add âSoÂŠ344028 tell this parableÂŠ344034 to the rebelliousÂŠ344033 Israeli people and explain that it comes from\add* the masterÂŠ344039 YahwehÂŠ344039:
\q1 Pour waterÂŠ344048 into the cooking pot and place it on the fire.
