\v 6 \add âNow\add* the masterÂŠ344084 YahwehÂŠ344084 saysÂŠ344082 this: The cityÂŠ344087 of bloodÂŠ344088 \add âwon't end well\add*â\add it's like\add* a cooking pot that has rust inÂŠ344092 it, and that rust won't come out of it. Take piece after piece out of it, butÂŠ344093 don'tÂŠ344094 \add âbe choosy about whichÂŠ344090 pieces\add*,
\v 7 because \add âthe bloodÂŠ344107 the city shed\add* is \add all the way\add* \add âthrough\add* itsÂŠ344108 centre. It \add âdisplayed the blood\add* on a flat rockÂŠ344113 \add to be easily seen\add*, rather than pouring it out on the ground where it could be coveredÂŠ344120 over withÂŠ344108 dust,
\v 8 \add âso it makes me angry enough to\add* get revengeÂŠ344127: IÂŠ344128 placed \em the city's\em* bloodÂŠ344131 on the smooth rockÂŠ344135, so it couldn't be coveredÂŠ344137.
\p
\v 9 Therefore, the masterÂŠ344143 YahwehÂŠ344143 saysÂŠ344142 this: The cityÂŠ344146 of bloodÂŠ344147 \add âwon't end well\add*. I'llÂŠ344151 also enlarge the pile of \add fire\add*wood \add to put underneath it\add*.
\v 10 \add âStack up\add* the wood and kindleÂŠ344156 the fireÂŠ344157. \add âCook the meat well\add* and mix in the spicesÂŠ344161 and let the bonesÂŠ344162 be charredÂŠ344163.
\v 11 ThenÂŠ344165 put the emptyÂŠ344169 pot onto \add the hot\add* coalsÂŠ344168 in order to heat andÂŠ344165 scorch its bronzeÂŠ344173, so the impurities in it will be meltedÂŠ344174âits corrosion \add âeaten away\add*.â
\v 12 \add ?âThat was a lot of work, butÂŠ344182\add* the fireÂŠ344188 didn'tÂŠ344182 remove the corrosion from it.
\v 13 Your shameful behaviour is in your uncleanness. Because you wouldn't \add âaccept it when\add* I tried to cleanseÂŠ344194 you, you won'tÂŠ344195 be purified anymore untilÂŠ344202 I've satisfiedÂŠ344204 my fury againstÂŠ344201 you.
\v 14 I, Yahweh, have declared it, and I will do it. I won'tÂŠ344215 relent, nor will I rest from it. \add âYou'll be judgedÂŠ344225 by your own practicesÂŠ344223 and your own behaviour\add*. That's the masterÂŠ344227 Yahweh'sÂŠ344211 declaration.â
