\v 4 so \add âbecause of that\add*, listen: I'm giving you to a peopleÂŠ344504 inÂŠ344512 the east as their possessionÂŠ344507. They'll set up camp against you and set up their tentsÂŠ344513 amongÂŠ344512 you. They'll eatÂŠ344515 your fruitÂŠ344516 and drinkÂŠ344518 your milkÂŠ344519.
