\v 6 Because the masterÂŠ344544 YahwehÂŠ344544 saysÂŠ344543 this: You clappedÂŠ344547 your hands and stampedÂŠ344549 your feetÂŠ344550 and celebrated withÂŠ344550 all the contempt within youÂŠ344547 against the \add âIsraeliÂŠ344558 nation\add*,
\v 7 therefore, listen \add Ammon\add*. I'll strike you \add âdown\add* and giveÂŠ344568 you as plunderÂŠ344570 to the \add other\add* nationsÂŠ344573. I'll cut you off from the peopleÂŠ344577 groups and make you perishÂŠ344578 from among the countriesÂŠ344581. I'll destroyÂŠ344582 you, and you'll knowÂŠ344583 that I am YahwehÂŠ344587.â
