\v 13 Therefore, the masterÂŠ344671 YahwehÂŠ344671 saysÂŠ344670: I'll hit EdomÂŠ344677 withÂŠ344686 my handÂŠ344674 and destroy every person and animalÂŠ344681 there. I'll make it a ruined, abandoned place, from TemanÂŠ344684 \add all the way\add* to DedanÂŠ344685âthey'll be killed by the swordÂŠ344686.
