\p
\v 1 \add âAt the beginning\add* of the monthÂŠ344772 inÂŠ344767 the eleventh yearÂŠ344770 \add since King Yoyakin (Jehoiachin) had been taken captive\add*, YahwehÂŠ344776 \add âgave me\add* a messageÂŠ344774:\x + \xo 26:1â28:19: \xt Yoel 3:4-8; Amos 1:9-10.\x*
\v 2 âHumanity's child, Tsor \add (TyreÂŠ344787)\add* has saidÂŠ344786 against Yerushalem, â\add âNice one\add*! \add âYerushalem'sÂŠ344790\add* gates are brokenÂŠ344792. \add âIt's going my wayâI can take advantage\add* becauseÂŠ344783 it's been destroyed.â
