\v 3 Because of that, the masterÂŠ344803 YahwehÂŠ344803 saysÂŠ344802 this: âListen, I'm opposed to you, Tsor, and I'llÂŠ344808 raise up many nationsÂŠ344810 against you, just like the seaÂŠ344813 raises itsÂŠ344814 wavesÂŠ344814.
\v 4 They'll destroyÂŠ344816 Tsor's wallsÂŠ344817 and tear down its towersÂŠ344820, thenÂŠ344816 I'llÂŠ344821 sweep its dust away and make it like a bare rockÂŠ344827.
