\v 5 Kush and PutÂŠ346495, Lydia, all ArabiaÂŠ346499, and LibyaÂŠ346500, together withÂŠ346505 the people belonging to the agreementÂŠ346503âthey'll all be killed by the swordÂŠ346505.
\v 6 Yahweh saysÂŠ346510 this: The ones who supportÂŠ346513 Egypt \add militarily\add* will fall, and the prideÂŠ346516 of \add @Egypt's\add* strengthÂŠ346517 will \add âcollapse\add*. From MigdolÂŠ346518 to Seveneh \add @their combined warriors\add* will be killed by the swordÂŠ346520. That's the masterÂŠ346525 Yahweh'sÂŠ346511 declaration.
\v 7 \add @Those allies\add* will be appalled in the midst of the abandoned landsÂŠ346530, andÂŠ346528 theirÂŠ346532 cities will be among all the \add other\add* ruined cities.
\v 8 ThenÂŠ346539 they'll knowÂŠ346539 that I am YahwehÂŠ346543, when I set fireÂŠ346546 to EgyptÂŠ346547, andÂŠ346548 when all itsÂŠ346551 helpersÂŠ346551 are destroyed.
\p
\v 9 \add âAt that time\add*, messengersÂŠ346556 will go out from in frontÂŠ346557 of me in shipsÂŠ346558 to terrorise Kush \add âwhen they think they're secureÂŠ346563\add*, and there'llÂŠ346570 be anguishÂŠ346565 among them onÂŠ346558 the day of Egypt'sÂŠ346568 doom. \add âYes, take notice,\add* it's comingÂŠ346571.
