\v 15 I'llÂŠ346663 pour out my fury on Egypt'sÂŠ346669 strongholdÂŠ346668 Pelusium \add (Heb. âSinÂŠ346667â)\add*, andÂŠ346670 cut off the crowdÂŠ346673 at ThebesÂŠ346674.
