\v 25 I'llÂŠ346831 strengthenÂŠ346831 the arms of the Babylonian king, while Far-oh's arms will fall. ThenÂŠ346831 they'll know that I am YahwehÂŠ346844, when I put my swordÂŠ346846 into the handÂŠ346847 of the king of BabylonÂŠ346836 andÂŠ346831 he \add âuses\add* it againstÂŠ346853 EgyptÂŠ346856.
