\v 9 I'llÂŠ347401 disturbÂŠ347401 the heartsÂŠ347402 of many peopleÂŠ347403 groups inÂŠ347405 lands thatÂŠ347411 you don'tÂŠ347412 know \add about\add*
\q1 when I bringÂŠ347405 about yourÂŠ347406 destructionÂŠ347406 among the nationsÂŠ347407âamong lands you haven't knownÂŠ347414.
