\p
\v 17 \add âIn the middle of that same monthÂŠ347545\add*,\f + \fr 32:17 \ft 585 B.C.\f* YahwehÂŠ347549 \add âgave me\add* a messageÂŠ347547:
\v 18 âHumanity's child, weep for the \add ânumerous Egyptians\add* and bringÂŠ347561 them down to the lowestÂŠ347569 partsÂŠ347569 of the earthÂŠ347568. \add âĄBring\add* \add @Egypt\add* and the daughtersÂŠ347563 of majestic nationsÂŠ347564 down along with thoseÂŠ347572 who've \add already\add* gone down into the pit.
\v 19 \add Ask them: Egypt,\add* are youÂŠ347576 really more beautiful than anyone else? Go down andÂŠ347578 lie down with the uncircumcisedÂŠ347581.
