\v 20 They'll fall among thoseÂŠ347584 who were killed by the sword. The sword has been drawnÂŠ347590. \add @Egypt\add* has been handed over to the swordâ\add @its enemies\add* will seize it and its multitudesÂŠ347594.
\v 21 The strongest of the warriors in \add âthe place of the dead\add* will declare about Egypt and its allies, âThey've comeÂŠ347606 down here. They'll lie with the uncircumcisedÂŠ347608âwith those who were killed by the swordÂŠ347611.â
