\v 22 AssyriaÂŠ347614 is thereÂŠ347613 with all its \add âpeople\add*, with its gravesÂŠ347619 all aroundÂŠ347618 itÂŠ347618âall of them were killed by the swordÂŠ347623.
\v 23 Those whose graves are set inÂŠ347628 the pit's recesses\x + \xo 32:23 \xt Isa 14:15.\x* are there, along withÂŠ347628 all itsÂŠ347632 \add âpeople\add*. ItsÂŠ347632 graves surround all of those who were killed by the swordÂŠ347638âthose who brought terrorÂŠ347642 onto the land of the livingÂŠ347644.
