\v 24 Eylam is thereÂŠ347646 with all its multitudesÂŠ347650, with its gravesÂŠ347652 all aroundÂŠ347651 itâall of them were killed. \add That's the place for\add* thoseÂŠ347675 who were killed by the swordÂŠ347656, who've gone down uncircumcisedÂŠ347660 to the lowestÂŠ347665 partsÂŠ347665 of the earthÂŠ347664, who brought their terrorsÂŠ347668 onto the land of the livingÂŠ347670, and who carry their own shame, together with the ones going down into the pit.
\v 25 They \add âprepared\add* a bed for Eylam and all its multitudesÂŠ347685 among those who were slainâits gravesÂŠ347687 surround it. All of them are uncircumcisedÂŠ347689, pierced by the swordÂŠ347692, becauseÂŠ347693 they brought their terrorsÂŠ347696 onto the land of the livingÂŠ347698. So they carry their own shame, together with the ones going down into the pit among all those who've been killed, those who are going down into the pit. \add @Eylam\add* is among all those who were killed.
\p
\v 26 MeshekÂŠ347710, Tuval, and all their multitudesÂŠ347714 are thereÂŠ347709 with their gravesÂŠ347716 all aroundÂŠ347715 them. All of them are uncircumcisedÂŠ347718, killed by the swordÂŠ347720, becauseÂŠ347721 theyÂŠ347723 brought their terrorsÂŠ347724 onto the land of the livingÂŠ347726.
\v 27 TheyÂŠ347738 don'tÂŠ347728 lie with the fallenÂŠ347733 warriors of the uncircumcisedÂŠ347734 who've gone down to \add âthe place of the dead\add* with all their weaponsÂŠ347739 of war, and with their swordsÂŠ347745 placed underÂŠ347746 their headsÂŠ347747 and their iniquitiesÂŠ347749 over their bonesÂŠ347752, becauseÂŠ347753 they were the terrorÂŠ347755 of warriors inÂŠ347739 the land of the livingÂŠ347758.
\p
\v 28 \add âSoÂŠ347760\add* youÂŠ347763, \add Egypt,\add* will be brokenÂŠ347763 amongst the uncircumcisedÂŠ347762. You'll lie alongside thoseÂŠ347767 who were pierced by the swordÂŠ347769.
\p
\v 29 EdomÂŠ347772 is \add also\add* there with its kingsÂŠ347773 and all its leaders. \add âDespite theirÂŠ347780 strengthÂŠ347780\add*, they've been placed with those killed by the swordÂŠ347785. They lie there along with the uncircumcisedÂŠ347789âwith those who've gone down into the pit.
