\v 30 All the northernÂŠ347798 leaders are there, along with all the SidoniansÂŠ347802 who went down with the ones who'd been pierced. They were powerful and made others afraid, butÂŠ347800 now they're there inÂŠ347809 shameâuncircumcisedÂŠ347814 along with those who were pierced by the swordÂŠ347819. They carry theirÂŠ347799 own shame, together with the ones going down into the pit.
