\v 31 Far-oh \add (PharaohÂŠ347829)\add* will look and be comfortedÂŠ347830 about all his multitudesÂŠ347835 who were pierced by the swordÂŠ347839âFar-oh and all his army. That'sÂŠ347840 the masterÂŠ347845 Yahweh'sÂŠ347846 declaration.
