\p
\v 1 Then YahwehÂŠ348509 \add âgave\add* me \add another\add* messageÂŠ348507:
\v 2 âHumanity's child, prophesy against Yisrael's shepherds. Prophesy and tell them that the masterÂŠ348529 YahwehÂŠ348529 says this to the shepherds: Yisrael's shepherds who are shepherding themselvesÂŠ348538 \add âwon'tÂŠ348539 end well\add*. Shouldn't shepherds guard the flockÂŠ348540?
\v 3 You eatÂŠ348547 the \add âbest sheepÂŠ348552 meat\add* andÂŠ348548 dress in \add âwoollen clothesÂŠ348551\add*. You slaughterÂŠ348553 the \add âfat lambs\add*. You don'tÂŠ348555 shepherdÂŠ348556 at all.
\v 4 You haven't \add âtaken care of those\add* with diseases, nor do you heal those who are ill. You don't bandage up the ones \add âwith broken limbs\add*, and you don't restore the outcasts or \add âsearch for those who've gone missing\add*. Instead, you use strengthÂŠ348562 and violence to rule over them.
\v 5 ThenÂŠ348587 they were scattered without a shepherdÂŠ348589, andÂŠ348587 after they were scattered, they becameÂŠ348590 food for all the \add âwild animalsÂŠ348594\add* in the countrysideÂŠ348595.\x + \xo 34:5: \xt Num 27:17; 1Ki 22:17; Mat 9:36; Mrk 6:34.\x*
\v 6 My flock has strayed across all the mountainsÂŠ348602 and onto everyÂŠ348604 highÂŠ348607 hill, and it's dispersed over the entireÂŠ348600 surfaceÂŠ348611 of the earthÂŠ348612, yet no one is searchingÂŠ348616 for them.
\p
\v 7 ThereforeÂŠ348621, you shepherdsÂŠ348621, listenÂŠ348622 to Yahweh'sÂŠ348626 messageÂŠ348625 \add to you\add*:
\v 8 This is the masterÂŠ348633 Yahweh'sÂŠ348634 declaration: As I live, my flock has become plunder and food for all the wild animalsÂŠ348649 in the countrysideÂŠ348650, because thereÂŠ348651 wasn't any shepherd and \add âĄbecause\add* none of my shepherds \add âtried to find any of\add* my flock \add that had gotten lost\add*. \add âInstead it was themselvesÂŠ348662 that\add* the shepherds looked after, and they didn'tÂŠ348637 shepherd my flock.
\v 9 ThereforeÂŠ348671, \add you so-called\add* âshepherdsâÂŠ348671, listenÂŠ348672 to Yahweh'sÂŠ348675 messageÂŠ348673:
\v 10 The masterÂŠ348680 YahwehÂŠ348680 says this: Listen, I'm againstÂŠ348683 those shepherds. I'll require \add âcompensation from them for\add* my flock, and then I'll dismiss them from shepherding the flock. Those shepherds won't shepherd themselvesÂŠ348699 any longer \add either\add*, \add âbecause\add* I'll take my flock away from theirÂŠ348702 mouthsÂŠ348702, so that my flock won't becomeÂŠ348705 food for them any longer.
\s1 The evil shepherds
