\v 23 I'llÂŠ348918 set one shepherd over themâmy servantÂŠ348925 DavidÂŠ348926. He'll \add âlook after\add* them, andÂŠ348918 he'll be their shepherd.\x + \xo 34:23: \xt Rev 7:17.\x*
\v 24 ThenÂŠ348936 I, Yahweh, will be theirÂŠ348944 godÂŠ348940, andÂŠ348941 my servantÂŠ348941 DavidÂŠ348942 will be a leader amongÂŠ348944 them. I, Yahweh, have declared that.\x + \xo 34:24: \xt Eze 37:24.\x*
\rem /s1 The Lord's Covenant of Peace
\p
\v 25 ThenÂŠ348949 I'llÂŠ348953 make a peaceÂŠ348952 treaty withÂŠ348961 them and remove the wild animalsÂŠ348954 from the land, so that they'll \add be able to\add* liveÂŠ348960 securelyÂŠ348962 in the wildernessÂŠ348961 and sleepÂŠ348963 safely in the forestsÂŠ348964.
\p
\v 26 I'llÂŠ348966 also \add âbless\add* \add both\add* them and the places aroundÂŠ348968 my hill, and sendÂŠ348971 out showers inÂŠ348973 the right seasonÂŠ348973âthey'll be showers of blessing.
\v 27 ThenÂŠ348978 the trees in the countrysideÂŠ348980 will produce their fruitÂŠ348983, the soil will yield itsÂŠ348986 produce, and my sheep will be secureÂŠ348991 in their land. WhenÂŠ348978 I breakÂŠ348997 \add âoff the ties holding the yoke\add* \add onto their necks\add*, and when I rescueÂŠ349002 them from the \add âcontrol\add* of thoseÂŠ349004 who enslavedÂŠ349004 them, thenÂŠ348978 they'll knowÂŠ348992 that I am YahwehÂŠ348996.
\v 28 They'll no longer be plunder for the \add other\add* nationsÂŠ349012, and the wild animalsÂŠ349013 on the land will no longer devourÂŠ349016 them. ThenÂŠ349007 they'll liveÂŠ349017 securelyÂŠ349018, and no one will \add âmake them afraid\add*.
\v 29 I'llÂŠ349022 provideÂŠ349022 a land for them that's known for its crops, so they won't be victims of famineÂŠ349031, andÂŠ349022 they won't be \add âmocked by\add* \add other\add* nationsÂŠ349038.
\v 30 ThenÂŠ349040 they'll know that I, Yahweh theirÂŠ349044 godÂŠ349044, am with them. The \add âIsraeliÂŠ349048 people\add* are my people. That's the masterÂŠ349051 Yahweh'sÂŠ349043 declaration.
\p
\v 31 You are my sheepÂŠ349055, the flockÂŠ349056 of my pastureÂŠ349057, and my people, and I am yourÂŠ349061 godÂŠ349061. That's the masterÂŠ349063 Yahweh'sÂŠ349064 declaration.â â
