\v 20 and the fish in the seaÂŠ350894 and the birds in the skiesÂŠ350896, the wild animalsÂŠ350897 in the countrysideÂŠ350898 includingÂŠ350895 all the creatures thatÂŠ350908 crawl on the earth, and every person who's on the surfaceÂŠ350911 of the land will trembleÂŠ350891 in front of me. The mountainsÂŠ350914 will be thrownÂŠ350913 down and the cliffsÂŠ350916 will fall, until every wallÂŠ350919 falls to the groundÂŠ350920.
\v 21 I'llÂŠ350923 summonÂŠ350923 \add âan army\add* against \add @Gog\add* onÂŠ350934 all my mountainsÂŠ350927. Every man's sword will be against his brotherÂŠ350934. That's the masterÂŠ350930 Yahweh'sÂŠ350931 declaration.
