\v 1 âNow, humanity'sÂŠ350975 child, prophesyÂŠ350976 against Gog and sayÂŠ350980 that the masterÂŠ350983 YahwehÂŠ350983 saysÂŠ350982 this: Listen, I'm against youÂŠ350986, Gog, leader of MeshekÂŠ350990 and Tuval.
