\v 17 Now, humanity's child, the masterÂŠ351268 YahwehÂŠ351268 says this to you: Tell all the winged birdsÂŠ351271 and all the wild animalsÂŠ351277 in the countrysideÂŠ351278, âGather together and comeÂŠ351280. Gather from all aroundÂŠ351282 to the sacrifice that I myself am making for youâa largeÂŠ351291 sacrifice on Yisrael's mountainsÂŠ351293, so that you can eat \add human\add* fleshÂŠ351296 and drinkÂŠ351297 bloodÂŠ351298.\x + \xo 39:17-20: \xt Rev 19:17-18.\x*
