\v 2 \add yes,\add* GodÂŠ351538 took me to YisraelÂŠ351543 in visionsÂŠ351537. He put me on a very highÂŠ351548 mountainÂŠ351547 \add where\add* there seemed to be cityÂŠ351553 buildings towards the southÂŠ351554,\x + \xo 40:2: \xt Rev 21:10.\x*
