\v 4 The manÂŠ351577 told me, âHumanity's child, look with your eyesÂŠ351582 and listenÂŠ351584 with your earsÂŠ351583, and fix your mindÂŠ351586 onÂŠ351582 everything that I'm revealing to you, becauseÂŠ351593 you were broughtÂŠ351596 here so I could reveal them to you. Report everything you see \add here\add* to the \add âIsraeliÂŠ351607 people\add*.â
