\p
\v 7 The leader's land will be on both sides of the area reserved for the holy place and the cityâon the west and the east. Its lengthÂŠ354475 will \add âbe the same as those portionsÂŠ354478 that it's parallelÂŠ354476 to\add*.
\v 8 That area will belongÂŠ354487 to Yisrael's leader \add so\add* the leaders won'tÂŠ354492 keep oppressingÂŠ354494 my peopleÂŠ354499, \add âbutÂŠ354492 rather\add* they'll giveÂŠ354501 the rest of the land to \add âbe divided among the tribesÂŠ354505\add*.
\rem /s1 Rules for the Prince
\v 9 The master Yahweh says this: \add âThat's plenty\add* for you, leaders of YisraelÂŠ354517! \add âReplace your\add* violenceÂŠ354519 and strife \add âwith\add* justiceÂŠ354521 and righteousnessÂŠ354522. Quit your evictionsÂŠ354525 of my peopleÂŠ354527. That's the master Yahweh'sÂŠ354512 declaration.
