\p
\v 18 The masterÂŠ354679 YahwehÂŠ354679 saysÂŠ354678 this: On the first \add dayÂŠ354682\add* of the first monthÂŠ354683 \add of the year\add*, youÂŠ354684 mustÂŠ354684 takeÂŠ354684 an unblemishedÂŠ354690 bullÂŠ354685 from the herd andÂŠ354691 perform a sinÂŠ354691 offering \add to purifyÂŠ354691\add* the temple.
\v 19 The priestÂŠ354697 will takeÂŠ354696 some of the bloodÂŠ354698 of that sinÂŠ354699 offeringÂŠ354699 and place it on the doorposts of the temple and on the fourÂŠ354707 cornersÂŠ354708 of the border of the altarÂŠ354710, and on the doorposts of the gateÂŠ354714 to the innerÂŠ354716 courtÂŠ354715.
