\p
\v 21 Then onÂŠ354731 the fourteenth day of that firstÂŠ354730 monthÂŠ354734, you \add Israelis\add* will have a seven-day celebration, \add âwhen you'll eat breadÂŠ354741 made without any raising agent\add*.\x + \xo 45:21: \xt Exo 12:1-20; Num 28:16-25.\x*
\v 22 That same dayÂŠ354746, the leader will prepare a bullÂŠ354754 as a sinÂŠ354755 offeringÂŠ354755 for himselfÂŠ354748 andÂŠ354744 for all the peopleÂŠ354752 in the country.
