\v 24 ThenÂŠ354777 the leader will perform a food offeringÂŠ354777 of twenty-two litres \add of flour\add* with seven litres of \add olive\add* oilÂŠ354783 for each bullÂŠ354779 andÂŠ354777 each ram.
\p
\v 25 On the fifteenth dayÂŠ354790 of the seventh monthÂŠ354791 \add of the year\add*, atÂŠ354788 the \add âtemporary sheltersâ\add* celebration, the leader will perform offerings onÂŠ354788 those sevenÂŠ354795 daysÂŠ354796: Sin offerings, burntÂŠ354798 offerings, food offerings, and offerings of oilÂŠ354800.\x + \xo 45:25: \xt Lev 23:33-36; Num 29:12-38.\x*
\c 46
